<ul>
<li class="toclevel-1"><a href="#Brief_history_of_East_India_Company_expansion_in_India"><span class="tocnumber">1</span> <span class="toctext">Brief history of East India Company expansion in India</span></a></li>
<li class="toclevel-1"><a href="#Causes_of_the_rebellion"><span class="tocnumber">2</span> <span class="toctext">Causes of the rebellion</span></a></li>
<li class="toclevel-1"><a href="#Onset_of_the_Rebellion"><span class="tocnumber">3</span> <span class="toctext">Onset of the Rebellion</span></a>
<ul>
<li class="toclevel-2"><a href="#Mangal_Pandey"><span class="tocnumber">3.1</span> <span class="toctext">Mangal Pandey</span></a></li>
