</div>
</div>
</td>
<td>
<div class="gallerybox" style="width: 155px;">
<div class="thumb" style="padding: 13px 0; width: 150px;">
<div style="margin-left: auto; margin-right: auto; width: 120px;"><a href="/wiki/File:Dalhousie.jpg" class="image" title="Dalhousie.jpg"><img alt="" src="http://upload.wikimedia.org/wikipedia/en/thumb/e/ef/Dalhousie.jpg/84px-Dalhousie.jpg" width="84" height="119" border="0" /></a></div>
</div>
