<li id="cite_note-11"><b><a href="#cite_ref-11" title="">^</a></b> <a href="#CITEREFMetcalfMetcalf2006" title="">Metcalf &amp; Metcalf 2006</a>, p.&#160;61</li>
<li id="cite_note-brownp88-12">^ <a href="#cite_ref-brownp88_12-0" title=""><sup><i><b>a</b></i></sup></a> <a href="#cite_ref-brownp88_12-1" title=""><sup><i><b>b</b></i></sup></a> <a href="#CITEREFBrown1994" title="">Brown 1994</a>, p.&#160;88</li>
